===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr|en}} {{term|acéphale|lang=fr}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|ἀκέφαλος||headless|tr=akephalos|lang=grc}}, from {{term|ἀ-||not|lang=grc}} + {{term|κεφαλή||head|tr=kephalē|lang=grc}}.

===Pronunciation===
